commit.message:
test: cover format_steps empty-input branch in aipm-pack wizard

Add a unit test that calls format_steps(&[]) to exercise the
True branch of the early-return guard at line 208:

    if steps.is_empty() {
        out.push_str("(no prompts)\n");
        return out;
    }

Before this test the branch was never triggered because every
other test passes the result of package_prompt_steps() which
always returns at least one step.

Branch coverage for aipm-pack/src/wizard.rs: 96.15% → 100%.
Overall workspace branch coverage: 92.90% → 92.95%.

